body:
I have a failure trying to use 2 for loop trying to index a multi dimension packed array :

```
$ iverilog -g2012  test.sv 
test.sv:10: error: A reference to a wire or reg (`i') is not allowed in a constant expression.
test.sv:10: error: Array index expressions must be constant here.
2 error(s) during elaboration.
```

```verilog
module test;

    reg [1:0][1:0] v;

    initial
    begin
        integer i,j;
        for (i=0; i<2; i=i+1)
            for (j=0; j<2; j=j+1)
                v[i][j] = 0;
    end

endmodule
```

